s="hps alt-edited">irr&eacute;gulier</span><span>), </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">la pression art&eacute;rielle basse</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">ou</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">l'hypertension art&eacute;rielle pas contr&ocirc;l&eacute;e</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">vous avez eu</span> <span class="hps">une attaque</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">cardiaque </span></span>au cours d<span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">es</span> <span class="hps">90 derniers jours</span>,<span class="hps alt-edited"> l'unsuffisance cardiaque ou un</span> <span class="hps">accident vasculaire c&eacute;r&eacute;bral</span>&nbsp;</span>pendant<span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps"> les</span> <span class="hps">6</span> <span class="hps">derniers mois</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"> <span class="hps">vous prenez un nitrate</span> <span class="hps atn">(</span><span>par exemple</span><span>, isosorbide, </span><span class="alt-edited">nitroglyc&eacute;rine</span><span>)</span> <span class="hps">en</span> <span class="hps atn">quelque forme (</span><span>par exemple, un comprim&eacute;</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">une g&eacute;lule,</span> une<span class="hps"> pommade) ou nitroprussiate</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">vous avez</span> <span class="hps">&eacute;t&eacute; inform&eacute; par votre</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">docteur d'&eacute;viter</span> <span class="hps">l'activit&eacute;</span> <span class="hps">sexuelle &agrave; cause de</span> <span class="hps">probl&egrave;mes cardiaques</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"> <span class="hps">vous utilisez</span> <span class="hps">certaines</span></span> m&eacute;dicaments<span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps"> r&eacute;cr&eacute;ationnelles appel&eacute;es</span> <span class="hps">poppers</span> <s